description: Jade Leader Corp. engages in the exploration and development of mineral properties in Canada and the United States. The company primarily explores for gold, copper, nickel, zinc, nephrite jade, and silver deposits. It holds a 100% interest in the Tell property that consists of 193 claims covering an area of 4,000 hectares located to the east of Mayo, Yukon; the DJ Jade project consisting 18 lode claims, which covers an area of approximately 140 hectares located in Washington State; and the Wyoming Jade Fields that consists of 99 mineral lode claims covering an area of 1,800 acres located in Wyoming. The company is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Jean-Pierre  Jutras B.Sc., B.Sc. Hons, P.Geo., P.Geol.
